Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:07.57,Title,,0,0,0,,{\be20\fade(800,0)\fs28\pos(185,370)}#13  {\fs48}Kings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,小黑 我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.07,0:00:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不許過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不會輸給你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,貓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,來了 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.32,0:01:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,比水流
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,起始之王 阿道夫．K．威斯曼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,伊佐那社
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.56,0:01:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎你來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你在劍上注入了強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,又如同湖面一般平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,能看得出你成長了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我也終於看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然你的劍法能變幻自如
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:02:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你的劍卻寄宿著堅定的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,能給予你強大力量的堅定意志
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,吾劍為綠之王的夙願而揮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,為白銀之王的願望而揮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,八田 還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,八田哥 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,室長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,淡島 到時候請不要猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,室長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,至少 讓他選擇死的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,老實說 我沒想到你能來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我也有堅強的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 上次我還沒來得及問你理由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,小白不會輸給你這種人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴 笨貓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,囉嗦 笨鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,雨乃雅日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是那場慘劇中倖存的少數幾人之一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,過去 迦具都玄示引起達摩克利斯之劍墜落的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我作為王覺醒一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她也得到了力量成為權外者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(412,425)}Strain
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 就像我失去性命一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她消除了自己的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,作為一隻貓活了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我們兩人被石板奪走了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,卻又獲得了嶄新的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,人類應該通過得到力量來保護自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,石板將這個願望實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不對 人類是無法駕馭石板的力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 你不相信人類嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的話 我就太失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,幻滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,過去的你明明相信著人類的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這樣的 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 根本不需要什麼石板的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小白小黑 還有其他所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就算沒有了那樣東西也能安然無恙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,貓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,之前雖然遇到過討厭的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,之後也應該還會遇上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 那時候所需要的東西並不是石板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,而是好吃的飯菜和...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一起吃飯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,吾輩想要的東西...是那些才對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,比水流 人類需要的東西並不是石板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只要...對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,小小的茶桌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只要這個就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我的結論
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,白銀之王的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,流 別沮喪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,流
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 接下來就該問你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,白銀之王到這裡來想幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我要破壞石板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎樣破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該最清楚石板的物理強度了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,再加上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓你碰它的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在與石板相連
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,能夠無窮盡地使用它的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至可以改寫白銀之王的不變之力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,將你殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我是無敵的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,室長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,安娜 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,八田哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不用管我 動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,安娜 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,現在開始 集結赤之氏族全體力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,為他開路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不留血跡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(320,425)}No Blood！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不留屍骨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(320,425)}No Bone！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不留灰燼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(320,425)}No Ash！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,全燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,全燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,全燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是你的計策嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真是更加讓我失望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,做這種事情有什麼用？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,路已經開通了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,路？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是...？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,正如你所猜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我要用達摩克利斯之劍墜落來破壞石板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 小狗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,現在能和我平分秋色了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 你現在不能只是平分秋色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不打贏我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不能去到你的王身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,展示給我看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這是小流的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,對 我的劍是屬於吾王的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是小白的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我在他的身邊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,御芍神紫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我會超越給你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,然後快點去你的王身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,山野間 異色繁花 同源三輪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:02.46,defination_ch,,0,0,0,,三輪：\N就佈施言，施者、受者和所施之物\N謂之三輪，行施後，此三輪相，不存於心\N名「三輪體空」。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道的俳句
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的俳句
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,您看到了嗎 一言大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那個孩子終於能獨當一面了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 我至少去撿起種子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你是認真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,居然用達摩克利斯之劍墜落...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,達摩克利斯之劍墜落能讓巨大的能量集中在一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.23,0:12:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,根據「舒貝爾特制御」第二方法論
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣會產生「共振音錘」效應
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(350,425)}Resonance Hammer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在計算了石板水平高度之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我發現這個臨界值正好與達摩克利斯之劍墜落的理論值相吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,只要符合固定條件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,石板和達摩克利斯之劍就能互相消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不會是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你竟然憑自己的意志改變威斯曼偏差值？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不會讓你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,從周防尊的事例來看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,從它崩壞到墜落地面為止需要十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,在此之前 只要殺掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,劍就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那你試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,別妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你一邊否定力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一邊卻能如此強大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,給我好好吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,注意禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我活下來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,室長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我挺感興趣淡島能不能斬殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說 辛苦妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,室長 請原諒我的無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,感謝還遠遠不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我很滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,流 流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他...死了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他是靠石板的力量而存活的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:16:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是誰在引起爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 能讓我收拾一下殘局嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,想不到你們還能從那種狀態下挽回局面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真是佩服的五體投地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經指示我們的氏族成員逃離這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.07,0:17:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你們也快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,磐先生 磐先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,流、流他...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你也走吧 琴坂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,贏了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,草薙哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,全員撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,任務完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看來我也...用盡...力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,現在這個身體不是我原本的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是學園島事件之前和無色之王交換的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說 這是他附身的某位少年的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:19:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我擁有白銀之王的不變之力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,才能一直使用這個身體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但這個力量已經消失了 和石板一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼？ 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼啊 小白？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然一直都借用這個身體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是得歸還給原主人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係的 我一定會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你們的...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,王...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,小白 小白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小白 小白 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,422)}小白 小白快醒醒 小白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:19:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你們是...誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,磐先生 流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,玩得開心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:25.96,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3\an7\fs20}Everything is no stop で走っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:30.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3\an7\fs20}Kiss your heart heart heart and 信じて to me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:36.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3\an7\fs20}Everywhere だって やってから蹴るんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:41.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3\an7\fs20}Kiss my heart heart heart and 信じた for you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:43.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3\an7\fs20}K life is a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:57.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3}エンドロールが流れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.12,0:21:02.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3}精一杯 fight fight 戦ったんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:08.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fade(50,50)\blur3}どうせ一杯抱いて 泣かないで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:12.84,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fade(50,50)\blur3}【We are and and and in this world】？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:19.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3}君にキスを 僕にキスを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:24.04,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3}どうか一人にしないでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:30.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fade(50,50)\blur3}いつか君と彩る世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:34.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fade(50,50)\blur3}Kiss your heart kiss my heart kiss this world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:40.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3}限界を突破して 全開で圧倒した
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.91,0:21:45.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3}目一杯燃やせ命を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:52.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3}さよならに変えないでよ 行かないでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:56.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3}誓うキズナ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:22:02.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fade(50,50)\blur3}絶対に絶命と絶好の到来を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.37,0:22:06.72,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fade(50,50)\blur3}何回も味も得たのは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:14.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fade(50,50)\blur3}君という掛け替えのない 代わりのいない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.65,0:22:19.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fade(50,500)\blur3}大事な色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:25.96,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3\an7\fs20}世間萬物不斷前行從不止步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:30.63,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3\an7\fs20}親吻君心 請相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:36.63,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3\an7\fs20}前路茫茫 只有啟程才能突破障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:41.07,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3\an7\fs20}親吻我心 我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:43.16,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3\an7\fs20}K 人生剎那光華
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:57.99,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3}只為終幕永不上映
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.12,0:21:02.57,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3}拼盡全力背水一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:08.56,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fade(50,50)\blur3}最終定會深情相擁 請抹去淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:12.84,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fade(50,50)\blur3}我們同在一個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:19.76,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3}為你獻吻 為我獻吻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:24.04,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3}請不要獨留我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:30.45,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fade(50,50)\blur3}我們終會為世界點上色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:34.74,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fade(50,50)\blur3}親吻君心 親吻我心 親吻世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:40.78,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fade(50,50)\blur3}突破界限 全力壓倒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.91,0:21:45.48,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fade(50,50)\blur3}燃盡生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:52.99,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fade(50,50)\blur3}再無永別 再無離去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:56.03,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fade(50,50)\blur3}以羈絆起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:22:02.06,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3}絕對的末路與良機到來之時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.37,0:22:06.72,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3}不斷回味個中的苦甜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:14.25,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,50)\blur3}屬於你的無可替換 無可代替
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.65,0:22:19.25,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fade(50,500)\blur3}珍貴的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.83,0:22:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.44,0:22:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.34,0:22:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:22:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.71,0:22:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.42,0:23:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 想不到吾輩會轉學進來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,而且還是這個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.66,0:23:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,請多關照 菊理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.37,0:23:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一起轉職進來的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.20,0:23:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,說是吾輩的親戚？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣設定的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,設定？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.11,0:23:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 他看上去是個挺有趣的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我們班都暱稱他作「德國老師」了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但是總覺得好像在哪裡見過他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.41,0:23:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了 肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,已經做好飯了 坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.72,0:23:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得吾輩的制服怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.87,0:23:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,妳早上就問過他了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.89,0:23:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很適合妳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.28,0:23:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.12,0:24:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
